goals.question: How does flight delay vary across different distance ranges?

```
import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    sns.histplot(data=data, x='delay', kde=True, color='blue')
    plt.axvline(x=data['delay'].mean(), color='red', linestyle='--', label='Mean Delay: {:.2f}'.format(data['delay'].mean()))
    plt.axvline(x=data['delay'].median(), color='green', linestyle='--', label='Median Delay: {:.2f}'.format(data['delay'].median()))
    plt.legend()
    plt.title('What is the distribution of flight delays?', wrap=True)
    plt.xlabel('Delay (minutes)')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

```
import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    sns.histplot(data=data, x='distance', kde=False, color='blue')
    plt.axvline(data['distance'].mean(), color='red', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label=f"Mean: {data['distance'].mean():.2f}")
    plt.axvline(data['distance'].median(), color='green', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label=f"Median: {data['distance'].median():.2f}")
    plt.legend()
    plt.title('What is the distribution of flight distances?', wrap=True)
    plt.xlabel('Distance')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
```

```
import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data = data.dropna()
    data = data.sort_values(by=['distance_range'])
    sns.countplot(x='distance_range', data=data, palette='Blues')
    plt.title('What is the most common distance range for flights?', wrap=True)
    plt.xlabel('Distance Range')
    plt.ylabel('Number of Flights')
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

```
import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data = data.dropna()
    sns.set(style="whitegrid")
    ax = sns.boxplot(x="distance_range", y="delay", data=data, palette="Set3")
    ax.set(xlabel='Distance Range', ylabel='Delay (minutes)')
    plt.title('How does flight delay vary across different distance ranges?', wrap=True)
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```
